  "secondary": {
    "description_full": "New remodeled house, kitchen, Basement GYM, Dinning Space are available to guests. the best location of Queens, it will satisfy all your needs for short or long time stay . Transportation is more convenient for Bus and LIRR train to Manhattan in 35 mins, quiet neighbor.\n\n I will be present in the house during your stay, and give your 24 hours satisfied support and answer your all question promptly. living room and kitchen are all equipped and ready for your sharing.\n\nThe space\nthis is kindly of small room for only one person and twin bed has set up, guest will have his/her own private bathroom which is located in down stair next to GYM\n\nGuest access\nguest could use kitchen and kitchen utensils, free access to dinning space and down stair GYM\n\nOther things to note\nplease wash clear after use kitchen and kitchen accessories \ndon't throw paper or tissue to toilet to avoid sewer pipe clog, thank you for cooperation.\n\nRegistration Details\nOSE-STRREG-0001096",
